<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.5.11">
<l>māri māṟāta taṇṇamalai vēṅkaṭat taṇṇalai</l>
<l>vāri māṟāta paimpūm poḻilcūḻ kurukūrnakar</l>
<l>kāri māṟaṉ caṭakōpaṉ collāyirat tippattāl</l>
<l>vēri māṟāta pūmē liruppāḷ viṉaitīrkkumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Through these ten in the thousand composed by Kāri Māṟaṉ Caṭakōpaṉ</l>
<l>from the city of Kurukūr surrounded by groves of fresh flowers where the waters do not change</l>
<l>on the majesty from Vēṅkaṭam, the cool mountain on which the showers do not change</l>
<l>she who sits on the flower that does not change in perfume put an end to karma.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
